OL,3,CScottish Finance Secretary requests
OL,4,Curgent meeting with Chancellor before
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FIt comes after a pre-Budget speech
OL,8,Ffrom the Chancellor in which she
OL,9,Ffailed to rule out tax rises, warning
OL,10,Fshe will have to make "necessary
OL,11,Fchoices" after the "world has thrown
OL,12,Fmore challenges our way".
OL,14,FReports later suggested the Chancellor
OL,15,Fcould raise income tax. The Fraser of
OL,16,FAllander Institute has estimated a 2p
OL,17,Fhike could cut Scotland's budget by #1
OL,18,Fbillion.
