OL,7,FThe Finance Secretary said: "The
OL,8,FChancellor's unexpected Downing Street
OL,9,Fspeech has fuelled speculation and
OL,10,Fpiled uncertainty on uncertainty about
OL,11,FLabour tax hikes in the upcoming UK
OL,12,FBudget, with a potential price tag of
OL,13,F#1 billion for Scotland.
OL,15,F"Let me be clear: Scotland should not
OL,16,Fbe left paying the price for Labour's
OL,17,Fbroken promises."
