OL,3,CScottish Finance Secretary requests
OL,4,Curgent meeting with Chancellor before
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FShe said: "This year, I am setting
OL,8,Fthree tests the UK Budget must meet `
OL,9,Fand the first is that the Chancellor
OL,10,Fmust ditch her outdated, restrictive
OL,11,Ffiscal rules. The era in which these
OL,12,Frules were set is over and Rachel
OL,13,FReeves must face up to the new reality.
OL,15,F"And crucially, every single penny
OL,16,Fraised from any Labour tax rises must
OL,17,Fbe invested into public services with
OL,18,Fconsequential funding for Scotland.
OL,26,@oD@KOUwD@AOU
