OL,3,CScottish Finance Secretary requests
OL,4,Curgent meeting with Chancellor before
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,F"Rachel Reeves must also confirm that
OL,8,FScotland will not see our funding cut
OL,9,Fas a result of Labour decisions.
OL,11,F"They came to office promising an end
OL,12,Fto austerity, so to impose it on
OL,13,FScotland would be a political betrayal
OL,14,Ffrom which Labour would never recover.
OL,16,F"I have requested an urgent meeting
OL,17,Fwith the Chancellor and will be clear
OL,18,Fto her that her Budget must meet these
OL,19,Fthree key tests.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
