OL,7,F"But the chaos and confusion coming
OL,8,Fout of the UK Government this week is
OL,9,Fjust confirmation that Scotland
OL,10,Fshouldn't be leaving crucial decisions
OL,11,Fabout our finances in the hands of
OL,12,Fincompetent Westminster governments `
OL,13,Fthese decisions should be in
OL,14,FScotland's hands, with the fresh start
OL,15,Fof independence."
OL,17,FAn HM Treasury spokesperson said: "Our
OL,18,Frecord funding settlement for Scotland
OL,19,Fwill mean over 20% more funding per
OL,20,Fhead than the rest of the UK.
