OL,7,F"We have also confirmed #8.3 billion
OL,8,Fin funding for GB Energy-Nuclear and
OL,9,FGB Energy in Aberdeen, up to #750
OL,10,Fmillion for a new supercomputer at
OL,11,FEdinburgh University, and are
