OL,13,Ffor City and Growth Deals across
OL,14,FScotland.
OL,16,F"This investment is all possible
OL,17,Fbecause our fiscal rules are non-
OL,18,Fnegotiable, they are the basis of the
OL,19,Fstability which underpins growth."
